# Festag — Tagro field assist

When adding or changing a Tagro assist bubble next to an input/textarea:

## Contract

1. **Typing lives in the real field** — never a second textarea inside the popup.
2. **Popup opens only on field focus/click** — not on page load / autoFocus alone.
3. **Freely draggable** — drag handle / head; remember user position until close.
4. **Do not steal focus** from the field; do not cover the field with a blocking backdrop.
5. **Outside-click closes** the popup, but clicks on the anchor field keep it open.
6. **Modes** rewrite the field text and insert back: at least **Formell** and **Sprachlich** (plus optional Tagro model). Mic writes into the same field.

## Pattern

```tsx
<textarea
  ref={fieldRef}
  value={value}
  onChange={e => setValue(e.target.value)}
  onFocus={() => setAssistOpen(true)}
/>
<TagroFieldAssist
  open={assistOpen}
  onClose={() => setAssistOpen(false)}
  anchorRef={fieldRef}
  fieldValue={value}
  onFieldChange={setValue}
  theme={theme}
/>
```

Canonical implementation: `components/auth/TagroFieldAssist.tsx`.
Do not reintroduce an in-popup draft input for this pattern.
